data.description: Bank-approved price! Before submitting any offer, please text agent for detailed instructions and to download the REQUIRED Amendment. Magnificently Renovated and Dazzling Ranch in Port Neches! Nestled on a corner lot in a desirable area, this 4BR/2BA, 1,564sqft home offers a modern farmhouse vibe with a sprawling covered front porch, classic board and batten siding, and a crisp white exterior. Explore the sundrenched interior to discover an openly flowing floorplan, a designer color scheme, stunning wood floors, a large living room, and a new entertainment-ready kitchen featuring a stainless- steel electric range/oven, quartz countertops, white shaker cabinetry, a gorgeous tile backsplash, and a dining area. Perfectly contrived for relaxation, the primary bedroom impresses with a custom walk-in closet and a spa-inspired en suite with a shower/tub combo, premium finishes, and a storage vanity.
